Hopefully, next year when we get to the playoffs we will remember what got us there. GO RAVENS.

Historical it's a Short career for these guys.
These types take away from the rest of the offense. They take away the running backs body of work and wr suffer from the lovs that lay them out to get hit.
The lineman have to work for longer per down.
Ill take a prolific NFL qb and style over any runner qb anyday.
Last every defender in the NFL has played most of their careers against the option and QB runners. They all know it to well and they always copycat from each team that finds ways to break these guys into.

snippet.textDisplay: I’m glad they lost. Stay humble kid. I didn’t necessarily like how he dissed the pro bowl. The pro bowl needs to be considered a great honor and it’s always taken into consideration when being chosen for the hall of fame. Think about it, Dan Marino never won a SB but he’s in the HOF. Nick Foles had an outstanding time with the eagles and won a SB, but will probably never be in the HOF. I think it’s all safe to say we respect Dan a hell of a lot more than Foles. (From an eagles fan). Sure you need a first place mentality to be first, but this kid is still young. He should aspire to be great every year with or without a ring
